                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391021-name-967" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-967" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-967" type="surname" value="BELLIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-967" type="given" value="HANNAH"></interp>HANNAH BELLIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am twelve years old; I live with my father, James Bellis, a butcher. On the 12th of October, I had my little sister, Sarah Ann Bellis, in my arms, on Stepney-green—the prisoner came, and snatched at the necklace she had on—he hurt her neck the first time, and the second time he got it and ran away—I ran after him, crying, "Stop thief," and the policeman took him.</p>
